finition","text":"adj. 智慧的(wise, discerning) n. 智者(a very wise person)"},{"type":"text","text":"The sage, by definition, possesses wisdom; the virtuoso, by definition,"},{"type":"text","text":"[serd3]"},{"type":"text","text":"possesses expertise."},{"type":"entry","text":"intimate","headword":"intimate"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 亲密的(closely acquainted) n.密友(an intimate friend or companion)"},{"type":"text","text":"[intrmat]"},{"type":"entry","text":"underscore","headword":"underscore"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 在-- 下面i国j线(to draw a line under); 强调(to make evident)"},{"type":"text","text":"[Andar'sko:r]"},{"type":"text","text":"图组合词：under（在.下面）+score（画线）→在.下面画线"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 模范，典范(a model of excellence or perfection)"},{"type":"entry","text":"paragon","headword":"paragon"},{"type":"text","text":"['paeraga:n]"},{"type":"note","text":"图词根记忆：para（超）+gon（角）→超过一般的顶尖人物→模范，典范"},{"type":"entry","text":"rudimentary","headword":"rudimentary"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.初步的(fundamental,elementary)：未充分发展的"},{"type":"text","text":"[ru:dr'mentri]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：rudi（无知的，粗鲁的）+ment+ary→无知状态→初步的"}]},{"number":128,"blocks":[{"type":"title","text":"Word List 10 >>>"},{"type":"entry","text":"disdain","headword":"disdain"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 轻视，鄱视(to refuse or reject with aloof contempt or scorn) n. 轻视，鄙视"},{"type":"text","text":"[dis'dern]"},{"type":"text","text":"(contempt)"},{"type":"note","text":"圆词根记忆：dis（不）+dain（看作dign，高贵）→把人弄得不高贵→轻视"},{"type":"text","text":"disdain for 轻视"},{"type":"text","text":"contemn, despise"},{"type":"entry","text":"invalidate","headword":"invalidate"},{"type":"text","text":".使无效，使作废（to make invalid）"},{"type":"text","text":"[1n'vaelidert]"},{"type":"text","text":"Strindberg's plays are marked by his extreme misogyny: he felt modern"},{"type":"text","text":"woman needed to dominate man and by subordinating him invalidate his"},{"type":"text","text":"masculinity."},{"type":"entry","text":"prototype","headword":"prototype"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 原型(an original model; archetype); 典型(a standard or typical example)"},{"type":"text","text":"['prautatarp]"},{"type":"note","text":"圆词根记忆：proto（起初）+type(形状）→起初的形状→原型"},{"type":"text","text":"留 This project is the first step in a long-range plan of research whose ultimate"},{"type":"text","text":"goal, still many years off, is the creation of a new prototype."},{"type":"entry","text":"undercut","headword":"undercut"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.削价（与竞争者）抢生意（to sell goods or services more cheaply than a"},{"type":"text","text":"[Andar'kAt]"},{"type":"text","text":"competitor)"},{"type":"text","text":"园组合词：under（在下面）+cut（砍）→偷愉把价格砍掉→削价（与竞争者）抢生意"},{"type":"entry","text":"recoil","headword":"recoil"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 弹回，反冲(to fall back under pressure);退却，退编(to shrink back physically"},{"type":"text","text":"[rr'korl]"},{"type":"text","text":"or emotionally)"},{"type":"note","text":"图词根记忆：re（反）+coil（卷，盘绕）→卷回去→退缩"},{"type":"entry","text":"evocative","headword":"evocative"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj唤起的，激起的（tending to evoke)"},{"type":"text","text":"[r'va:katrv]"},{"type":"text","text":"The documentary film about high school life was so realistic and evocative"},{"type":"text","text":"that feelings of nostalgia flooded over the college-age audience."},{"type":"entry","text":"dubious","headword":"dubious"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj可疑的（slightly suspicious about);有问题的，靠不住"},{"type":"text","text":"['du:bias]"},{"type":"text","text":"的(questionable or suspect as to true nature or quality)"},{"type":"note","text":"圆词根记忆：dub（二，双）+ious→两种状态→不肯定的"},{"type":"text","text":"怀疑的→可疑的"},{"type":"text","text":"dubious"},{"type":"text","text":"disputable, dubitable, equivocal, problematic"},{"type":"entry","text":"astute","headword":"astute"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 机敏的, 精明的(showing clever or shrewd mind, cunning: crafty)"},{"type":"text","text":"[a'stu:t]"},{"type":"text","text":"来自拉丁文as