trated) : 多孔的(full of pores)"},{"type":"text","text":"['po:ras]"},{"type":"text","text":"园来自pore（n.孔）"},{"type":"entry","text":"intrinsic","headword":"intrinsic"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.固有的，内在的，本质的(belonging to the essential nature)"},{"type":"text","text":"[rn'trinsik]"},{"type":"text","text":"In his address, the superintendent exhorted the teachers to discover and"},{"type":"text","text":"develop each student's intrinsic talents."},{"type":"text","text":"congenital, connate, elemental, inherent, innate"},{"type":"entry","text":"captious","headword":"captious"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 吹毛求疵的(quick to find fault; carping)"},{"type":"text","text":"['kaepfas]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：capt（拿）+ious→拿（别人的缺点）→吹毛求癌的"},{"type":"entry","text":"sordid","headword":"sordid"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 卑那的;肮脏的(cirty, filthy)"},{"type":"text","text":"['so:rdid]"},{"type":"text","text":"foul, mean, seedy"},{"type":"entry","text":"indict","headword":"indict"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.控诉，起诉（to make a formal accusation against:; accuse)"},{"type":"text","text":"[rn'dart]"},{"type":"note","text":"图词根记忆：in（进入）+dict（说）→进（法庭）讨个说法→控诉"},{"type":"text","text":"criminate, impeach, incriminate, inculpate"},{"type":"text","text":"indictment（n.起诉：控告）"},{"type":"entry","text":"awe","headword":"awe"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.敬畏(to cause a mixed feeling of reverence and fear)n.敬畏"},{"type":"text","text":"[p:]"},{"type":"text","text":"园发音记忆：发音像“噢”→表示敬畏的声音→敬畏"},{"type":"text","text":"图be in aweof对.·望而生畏；对.感到害怕"},{"type":"entry","text":"cryptic","headword":"cryptic"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 秘密的，神秘的(mysterious, bafling)"},{"type":"text","text":"['kriptrk]"},{"type":"note","text":"图词根记忆：crypt（秘密）+ic→秘密的"},{"type":"entry","text":"intransigent","headword":"intransigent"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 不妥协的(uncompromising)"},{"type":"text","text":"[rn'traenzidzant]"},{"type":"note","text":"图联想记忆：in（不)+transigent（妥协的）→不妥协的"},{"type":"text","text":"Always circumspect, she was reluctant to make judgments, but once arriving"},{"type":"text","text":"at a conclusion, she was intransigentin its defense."},{"type":"text","text":"incompliant, intractable, obstinate, pertinacious"},{"type":"text","text":"intransigence (n.不妥协，不让步)"},{"type":"entry","text":"upheaval","headword":"upheaval"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.动乱，剧变(extreme agitation or disorder)"},{"type":"text","text":"[Ap'hi:vl]"},{"type":"text","text":"园来自upheave[v（使）发生混乱]"},{"type":"entry","text":"despotic","headword":"despotic"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.专横的，暴虐的(autocratic, tyrannical)"},{"type":"text","text":"[dt'spa:trk]"},{"type":"text","text":"园来自despot（n.暴君）"}]},{"number":130,"blocks":[{"type":"title","text":"Word List 10 >>>"},{"type":"entry","text":"insouciance","headword":"insouciance"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.漠不关心，漫不经心（(lighthearted unconcern)"},{"type":"text","text":"[rn'su:sians]"},{"type":"note","text":"圆词根记忆：in（不）+souc（担心）+iance→不担心→漠不关心"},{"type":"entry","text":"mean","headword":"mean"},{"type":"definition","text":"adji. 各的 (selfish in a petty way; stingy)"},{"type":"text","text":"[mi:n]"},{"type":"text","text":"close-fisted, niggardly, miserly, ungenerous"},{"type":"entry","text":"obtuse","headword":"obtuse"},{"type":"definition","text":"adji. 愚笨的(dull, insensitive); 钝的(blunt)"},{"type":"text","text":"[ab'tu:s]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：ob（向）+tus（敲击）+e→用钝器敲击→钝的"},{"type":"text","text":"obtuseness（n.迟钝；感觉迟钝）"},{"type":"entry","text":"lopsided","headword":"lopsided"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.倾向—方的，不平衡的(lacking in symmetry or balance or proportion)"},{"type":"text","text":"[la:p'sardid]"},{"type":"text","text":"组合词：lop（低重）+side（侧面，边）+（e)d→垂向一边的→倾向一方的"},{"type":"entry","text":"nullify","headword":"nullify"},{"type":"text","text":". 使无效(to invalidate);抵消(to cancel out)"},{"type":"text","text":"['nAlrfar]"},{"type":"note","text":"园词根记忆：null（无）+ify（使）→使变成无→使无效"},{"type":"text","text":"nullification（n.无效：废弃）"},{"type":"entry","text":"epilogue","headword":"epilogue"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.收场白；尾声(a closing section)"},{"type":"text","text":"['eprlb:g]"},{"type":"note","text":"园词根记忆：epi（在后）+logue（说话）→在后面说的话→尾声"},{"type":"entry","text":"presage","headword":"presage"},{"type":"text","text":"['presrd3] n. 预(an intuition or feeling of the future)"},{"type":"text","text":"[prr'serd3] v. 预示(to foreshadow; foretell)"},{"type":"note","text":"图词根记忆：pre（预先）+sag（知道）+e→预先知道→预感"},{"type":"entry","text":"offish","headword":"offish"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 冷淡的(distant and reserved)"},{"type":"text","text":"[s:fi]"},{"type":"note","text":"圆联想记忆：off（离开）+（f)ish（鱼）→鱼离开了，池塘冷清→冷淡的"},{"type":"entry","text":"gaiety","headword":"gaiety"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.欢乐，快活（cheerfulness）"},{"type":"text","text":"[gerati]"},{"type":"text","text":"图来自gay（adj.欢乐的）"},{"type":"entry","text":"abound","headword":"abound"},{"type":"definition","text":"v大量存在(to be great in number or amount);充满，富于（to be fully supplied"},{"type":"text","text":"[a'baund]"},{"type":"text","text":"or filled of; teem with)"},{"type":"note","text":"园词根记忆：ab（加强）+ound（看作und，溢出）→溢出→充满"},{"type":"entry","text":"prescience","headword":"prescience"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.预知，先见(foreknowledge of events)"},{"type":"text","text":"['presians]"},{"type":"text","text":"国词根记忆：pre（预先）+sci（知道）+ence→预知，先见"},{"type":"entry","text":"gargantuan","headword":"gargantuan"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj巨大的，庞大的(of tremendous size or volume)"},{"type":"text","text":"[ga:r'gaentfuan]"},{"type":"text","text":"国来自法国作家拉伯雷的著作《巨人传》中的巨人Gargantua"},{"type":"text","text":"colossal, enormous, gigantic"},{"type":"entry","text":"peer","headword":"peer"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.同等之人，同辈(one belonging to the same societal group especially based"},{"type":"text","text":"[prr]"},{"type":"text","text":"on age, grade, or status)"},{"type":"entry","text":"occlude","headword":"occlude"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 使闭塞(to prevent the passage of)"},{"