de"},{"type":"text","text":"room."},{"type":"entry","text":"douse","headword":"douse"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.把浸入水中（to plunge into water)）;熄灭(to extinguish)"},{"type":"text","text":"[daus]"},{"type":"note","text":"园联想记忆：do（做）+use（用）→用水来做→把浸入水中"},{"type":"entry","text":"abash","headword":"abash"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 使羞愧，使尴尬(to make embarrassed)"},{"type":"text","text":"[a'ba]"},{"type":"note","text":"图联想记忆：ab+ash（灰）→脸上有灰→使尴尬"},{"type":"text","text":"unabashed（adj不在乎的：不难为情的）：unabashedly（adv.毫不掩饰地）"},{"type":"entry","text":"snobbish","headword":"snobbish"},{"type":"text","text":"adlj.势利眼的(being,characteristic of, or befiting a snob)：假充绅士的"},{"type":"text","text":"['sna:brj]"},{"type":"text","text":"圆来自snob（n.势利小人）"},{"type":"entry","text":"limp","headword":"limp"},{"type":"definition","text":"v跛行（to walk lamely)adj.软弱的，无力的(flaccid，drooping)：柔软的"},{"type":"text","text":"[lxmp]"},{"type":"text","text":"floppy, loose"},{"type":"entry","text":"idle","headword":"idle"},{"type":"text","text":"adj（指人）无所事事的（avoiding work)：无效的（useless)"},{"type":"text","text":"idle"},{"type":"text","text":"['ardl]"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.懒散，无所事事（to donothing)"},{"type":"text","text":"发音记忆：“爱斗”→无所事事的人才爱斗→无所事事"},{"type":"entry","text":"restrain","headword":"restrain"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.克制，抑制(to keep under control)"},{"type":"text","text":"[rt'strern]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：re（重新）+strain（拉紧）→重新拉紧→克制，"}]},{"number":132,"blocks":[{"type":"title","text":"Word List 10 >>>"},{"type":"entry","text":"compunction","headword":"compunction"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 便;良心不安(a sense of guilt; remorse; penitence)"},{"type":"text","text":"[kam'pank{n]"},{"type":"note","text":"园词根记忆：com（共同）+punct（点）+ion→浑身像针刺一样难受→懊悔"},{"type":"entry","text":"illustrious","headword":"illustrious"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 著名的，显赫的(very distinguished; outstanding)"},{"type":"text","text":"[r'lAstrias]"},{"type":"note","text":"图词根记忆：i（表加强）+lustr（光）+ious→光彩照人的→显赫的"},{"type":"entry","text":"grotesque","headword":"grotesque"},{"type":"text","text":"adj（外形或方式）怪诞的，古怪的（bizarre;fantastic）：（艺术等）风格怪异的"},{"type":"text","text":"[grau'tesk]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：grot（看作grotto，岩洞）+esque（看作picturesque，图画的）→岩润里"},{"type":"text","text":"怪诞的图画→（艺术等）风格怪异的"},{"type":"entry","text":"clement","headword":"clement"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 仁慈的(merciful)：温和的(mild)"},{"type":"text","text":"['klemant]"},{"type":"text","text":"clement weather温和的气候"},{"type":"entry","text":"august","headword":"august"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj威严的，令人敬畏的(impressive,majestic)"},{"type":"text","text":"[:gAst]"},{"type":"note","text":"联想记忆：八月（August）丰收大地金黄，金黄色是威严的帝王的象征→威严的"},{"type":"entry","text":"impasse","headword":"impasse"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 僵局(deadlock);死路(blind alley)"},{"type":"text","text":"[xmpaes]"},{"type":"note","text":"圆词根记忆：im（不）+pass通过）+e→通不过→僵局；死路"},{"type":"entry","text":"unassuming","headword":"unassuming"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.不摆架子的，不装腔作势的，谦逊的（not arrogant or presuming:modest)"},{"type":"text","text":"[Ana'su:mrn]"},{"type":"text","text":"过联想记忆：un(不)+assuming(傲慢的)→谦逊的"},{"type":"entry","text":"malfeasance","headword":"malfeasance"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 不法行为，渎职(misconduct by a public official)"},{"type":"text","text":"[mael’fi:zans]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：mal（坏的）+feas（做，行为）+ance→坏的行为→不法行为"},{"type":"entry","text":"pellucid","headword":"pellucid"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj清蜥的，清激的(transparent, clear)"},{"type":"text","text":"[pa'lu:sid]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：pel（看作per，全部)+luc（光）+id→光线充足的→清晰的"},{"type":"text","text":"pellucidity（n.透明度，透明性）"},{"type":"entry","text":"hubris","headword":"hubris"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.傲慢，目中无人(overbearing pride or presumption; arrogance)"},{"type":"text","text":"['hju:brrs]"},{"type":"note","text":"联想记忆：hub（中心）+ris（看作rise，升起）→中心升起→以（自我）为中心→目中"},{"type":"text","text":"无人"},{"type":"entry","text":"arrogance","headword":"arrogance"},{"type":"text","text":"hubristic (acj. 做慢的)"},{"type":"entry","text":"riveting","headword":"riveting"},{"type":"text","text":"adlj.非常精彩的，引|人入胜的(engrossing.fascinating)"},{"type":"text","text":"['rrvitin]"},{"type":"text","text":"The English novelist Wiliam Thackeray considered the cult of the criminal so"},{"type":"text","text":"dangerous that he criticized Dickens’ Oliver Twist for making the characters in"},{"type":"text","text":"the thieves’ kitchen so riveting."},{"type":"entry","text":"deprivation","headword":"deprivation"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 剥夺(removal from an office, dignity. or benefice)： 丧失(the state of being"},{"type":"text","text":"[deprr'ver{n]"},{"type":"text","text":"deprived)"}]},{"number":133,"blocks":[{"type":"text","text":"<<GRE词汇精选乱序版"},{"type":"entry","text":"integral","headword":"integral"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj构成整体所必需的（necessary for completeness)：完整的（whole）"},{"type":"text","text":"['intrgral]"},{"type":"note","text":"图词根记忆：in（不）+tegr（触摸）+al→未被触摸的→完整的"},{"type":"entry","text":"contiguous","headword":"contiguous"},{"type":"definition","text":"ad接填的：接近的（near，adjacent)"},{"type":"text","text":"[kan'trgjuas]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：con（共同）+tig（接触）+uous→共同接触→接近的"},{"type":"text","text":"图be contiguous with与.-接壤"},{"type":"entry","text":"abject","headword":"abject"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 极可怜的(miserable, wretched); 单下的(degraded, base)"},{"type":"text","text":"['ebdzekt]"},{"type":"text","text":"国词根记忆：ab（去掉）+ject（抛，扔）→被人扔掉→极可怜的"},{"type":"entry","text":"shrewd","headword":"shrewd"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 机灵的，精明的(marked by clever discerning awareness)"},{"type":"text","text":"[ru:d]"},{"type":"text","text":"园注意不要和shrew（n.泼妇）相混"},{"type":"entry","text":"dismantle","headword":"dismantle"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 拆除 (to take a part, disassemble)"},{"type":"text","text":"[drs'maentl]"},{"type":"note","text":"图词根记忆：dis（除去）+mantle（覆盖物）→拆掉覆盖物→拆除"},{"type":"entry","text":"culprit","headword":"culprit"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 罪(one who is guilty of a crime)"},{"type":"text","text":"['kAlprrt]"},{"type":"note","text":"联想记忆：犯罪（sin）的人被称为罪犯（culprit）"},{"type":"entry","text":"assuage","headword":"assuage"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.缓和，减轻(to lessen, relieve)"},{"type":"text","text":"[a'swerd3]"},{"type":"note","text":"园词根记忆：as（使）+suage（甜）→变甜→缓和"},{"type":"entry","text":"lumber","headword":"lumber"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.跌跌撞撞地走，笨拙地走（to move with heavy clumsiness）n.杂物"},{"type":"text","text":"[lambar]"},{"type":"text","text":"(miscellaneous discarded household articles); 本材 (timber)"},{"type":"entry","text":"obeisance","headword":"obeisance"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.郸躬，敬礼(a gesture of respect or reverence)"},{"type":"text","text":"[au'bi:sns]"},{"type":"note","text":"园词根记忆：obeis看作obed，服从）+ance→服从的态度→敬礼"},{"type":"entry","text":"choleric","headword":"choleric"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 易怒的,暴躁的(having irascible nature, irritable)"},{"type":"text","text":"[ka:lark]"},{"type":"note","text":"图词根记忆：choler(胆汁）+ic→胆汁质的→易怒的，暴躁的"},{"type":"entry","text":"spate","headword":"spate"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.许多，大量（a large number or amount)：（水流）暴涨，发洪水（flood）"},{"type":"text","text":"[spert]"},{"type":"text","text":"图aspateof一连串，接二连三（通常指不愉快的事物）"},{"type":"entry","text":"invoke","headword":"invoke"},{"type":"definition","text":"v祈求，悬求(to implore, entreat);使生效(to put into effect or operation use)"},{"type":"text","text":"[In'vauk]"},{"type":"note","text":"圆词根记忆：in（使）+vok（叫喊）+e→使有发言权→使生效"},{"type":"entry","text":"predilection","headword":"predilection"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 偏爱, 嗜好 (a special liking that has become a habit)"},{"type":"text","text":"[predl'ek{n]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：pre（在前）+di（分开)+lect(选择）+ion→在之前就做出了选择→偏爱，"},{"type":"text","text":"嗜好"},{"type":"entry","text":"exiguous","headword":"exiguous"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.太少的，不足的(scanty, meager)"},{"type":"text","text":"[eg'zigjuas]"},{"type":"text","text":"scarce, skimpy. sparse"},{"type":"text","text":"exiguity (n.稀少：微小）"},{"type":"entry","text":"acumen","headword":"acumen"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 敏锐, 精明(keenness and depth of perception)"},{"type":"text","text":"['aekjaman]"},{"type":"note","text":"图词根记忆：acu（尖，锐利）+men（表抽象名词）→敏锐，精明"}]},{"number":134,"blocks":[{"type":"title","text":"Word List 10 >>>"},{"type":"entry","text":"provenance","headword":"provenance"},{"type":"text","text":"['pra:vanans]"},{"type":"note","text":"图词根记忆：pro（前面）+ven（来）+ance→前面来的东西→起源"},{"type":"entry","text":"redolent","headword":"redolent"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj芬芳的，芳香的（scented，aromatic）"},{"type":"text","text":"[redalant]"},{"type":"note","text":"图词根记忆：red（看作re，加强）+ol（气味）+ent→散发出浓郁的气味→芳香的"},{"type":"entry","text":"particularize","headword":"particularize"},{"type":"definition","text":"v 详述，列举(to give the details of sth. one by one)"},{"type":"text","text":"[par'trkjalaraiz]"},{"type":"text","text":"图来自particular（adj.详细的）"},{"type":"entry","text":"liken","headword":"liken"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 把比作(to compare to)"},{"type":"text","text":"['larkan]"},{"type":"text","text":"国来自like（prep.像）"},{"type":"entry","text":"discern","headword":"discern"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 识别),看出(to recognize as separate or different; distinguish)"},{"type":"text","text":"[dr’ss:rn]"},{"type":"note","text":"图词根记忆：dis（加强）+cem（区别）→一再区别→识别"},{"type":"text","text":"disceming（adj.有洞察力的）"},{"type":"entry","text":"jeopardy","headword":"jeopardy"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 危险(great danger, peril)"},{"type":"text","text":"['dgepardi]"},{"type":"text","text":"injeopardy处于危险境地，受到威胁"},{"type":"entry","text":"extinguish","headword":"extinguish"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.使熄灭(to cause to cease burming)：使--不复存在(to end the existence of)"},{"type":"text","text":"[rk'strngwj]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：ex（出）+tingu（看作sting，刺）+ish→把刺拔出，刺引l申为火焰→使熄灭"},{"type":"entry","text":"pertain","headword":"pertain"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 属于(to belong as a part): 关于(to have reference)"},{"type":"text","text":"[par'tein]"},{"type":"note","text":"园词根记忆：per（始终）+tain（拿住）→始终都拿在手里→属于"},{"type":"entry","text":"liability","headword":"liability"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 责任(the state of being liable);债务(obligation, debt)"},{"type":"text","text":"[,lara'brlati]"},{"type":"note","text":"圆词根记忆：（看作lig，捆）+ability→将人捆住→责任"},{"type":"entry","text":"rote","headword":"rote"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 死记硬情(a memorizing process using routine or repetition, often without full"},{"type":"text","text":"[raut]"},{"type":"text","text":"attention or comprehension)"},{"type":"note","text":"园词根记忆：rot（转）+e→摇头晃脑地转着背→死记硬背"},{"type":"entry","text":"fertile","headword":"fertile"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj多产的(productive,fecund);肥沃的"},{"type":"text","text":"['f3:rtl]"},{"type":"note","text":"图词根记忆：fert（看作fer，带来）+ile→带来果实的→多产的"},{"type":"entry","text":"recant","headword":"recant"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 撤回(声明)，放弃(信仰Xto withdraw or repudiate a statement or belief)"},{"type":"text","text":"[r'kaent]"},{"type":"note","text":"图词根记忆：re（反）+cant（唱）→唱反调→放弃（信仰）"},{"type":"entry","text":"modicum","headword":"modicum"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 少量(a moderate or small amount)"},{"type":"text","text":"图amodicum of一点，少数"},{"type":"text","text":"['mo:drkam]"},{"type":"entry","text":"wily","headword":"wily"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj诡计多端的，狡的(full of wiles; crafty)"},{"type":"text","text":"来自wile（n.诡计）"},{"type":"text","text":"[warli]"},{"type":"entry","text":"rabid","headword":"rabid"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj患狂犬病的(affected with rabies)：疯狂的，狂暴的(going to extreme lengths"},{"type":"text","text":"['raebid]"},{"type":"text","text":"in expressing or pursuing a feeling. interest or opinion)"},{"type":"text","text":"来自rabies（n.狂犬病）"},{"type":"entry","text":"diffuse","headword":"diffuse"},{"type":"definition","text":"v散布，(光等）湿射(to disperse in every direction）ad.漫射的，散漫的（spreading"},{"type":"text","text":"[dxfju:s]"},{"type":"text","text":"out or dispersed)"}]},{"number":135,"blocks":[{"type":"text","text":"K<<GRE词汇精选乱序版"},{"type":"entry","text":"adjudicate","headword":"adjudicate"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 充当裁判(to serve as a judge in a dispute); 判决(to settle judicially)"},{"type":"text","text":"[a'dzu:drkert]"},{"type":"text","text":"国词根记忆：ad（加强）+jud（判断）+icate→不断判断→充当裁判"},{"type":"entry","text":"skullduggery","headword":"skullduggery"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.欺骗，使诈(underhanded or unscrupulous behavior)"},{"type":"text","text":"[skAl'dngari]"},{"type":"note","text":"联想记忆：skull（头颅，脑袋）+dug（挖）+gery→挖脑袋→想方设法作假→欺骗，"},{"type":"text","text":"使诈"},{"type":"entry","text":"blemish","headword":"blemish"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.损害：玷污(to mar;spoil the perfection of)n.瑕疵，缺点(defect)"},{"type":"text","text":"[blemxj]"},{"type":"note","text":"圆词根记忆：blem（弄伤）+ish→把-弄伤→损害；玷污"},{"type":"text","text":"unblemished（adj.毫无瑕疵的；完好的）"},{"type":"entry","text":"exalt","headword":"exalt"},{"type":"definition","text":"v赞扬，歌颂(to praise: glorify: extol)"},{"type":"text","text":"[rg'z>:lt]"},{"type":"note","text":"园词根记忆：ex（向上）+alt（高）→向上抬高→赞扬"},{"type":"text","text":"exaltation（n.得意，高兴）"},{"type":"entry","text":"parochial","headword":"parochial"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj教区的(of or relating to a church parish);地方性的，获小的(restricted to a"},{"type":"text","text":"[pa'raukial]"},{"type":"text","text":"small area or scope; narrow)"},{"type":"text","text":"parochialism (n.狭隘)"},{"type":"entry","text":"monolithic","headword":"monolithic"},{"type":"text","text":"adlj.坚若磐石的：巨大的（huge,massive)"},{"type":"text","text":"[,ma:na'lrθrk]"},{"type":"note","text":"图词根记忆：mono（单个的）+lith（石头）+ic→单块大石头的→巨大的"},{"type":"entry","text":"fathom","headword":"fathom"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.英寻v彻底了解，弄清真相（to understand thoroughly)"},{"type":"text","text":"[fedam]"},{"type":"text","text":"fathomless（adj.深不可测的，无法理解的）"},{"type":"entry","text":"onset","headword":"onset"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.开始，发作(beginning,commencement);攻击，袭击（attack，assault)"},{"type":"text","text":"['a:nset]"},{"type":"text","text":"Although adolescent maturational and developmental states occur in an"},{"type":"text","text":"orderly sequence, their timing varies with regard to onsef and duration."},{"type":"entry","text":"indignant","headword":"indignant"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.愤概的，愤债不平的（feeling or expressing anger)"},{"type":"text","text":"[xn'dignant]"},{"type":"text","text":"angry"},{"type":"entry","text":"tempestuous","headword":"tempestuous"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.狂暴的(turbulent, stormy)"},{"type":"text","text":"[tem'pestfuas]"},{"type":"text","text":"图a tempestuousrelationship冲突不断的关系"}]},{"number":136,"blocks":[{"type":"title","text":"Word List 10 >>>"},{"type":"entry","text":"plentitude","headword":"plentitude"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 充分(the quality or state of being full)"},{"type":"text","text":"['plentrtu:d]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：plent（满）+itude→充分"},{"type":"entry","text":"flighty","headword":"flighty"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj轻浮的（skittish)：反复无常的（capricious）"},{"type":"text","text":"[flarti]"},{"type":"note","text":"联想记忆：f+light（轻的）+y→因为轻而飘浮着→轻浮的"},{"type":"entry","text":"roost","headword":"roost"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. (乌类的)栖息效(a place where winged animals, especially birds or bats, rest or"},{"type":"text","text":"[ru:st]"},{"type":"text","text":"sleep) v 栖息(to rest or sleep on a perch or in a roost)"},{"type":"entry","text":"omnivore","headword":"omnivore"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 杂食动物(an animal or a person that eats all types of food, especially both"},{"type":"text","text":"[a:mnIv>:r]"},{"type":"text","text":"plants and meat)"},{"type":"text","text":"→杂食动物"},{"type":"entry","text":"amplify","headword":"amplify"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.放大(to make larger;extend)：详述(to develop with"},{"type":"text","text":"['aemplrfar]"},{"type":"text","text":"details)"},{"type":"note","text":"园词根记忆：ampl（大）+ify→放大"},{"type":"text","text":"amplify"}]}]}